# Infrastructure Engineer Lab Portfolio

Welcome to my Infrastructure Engineer Home Lab Portfolio.

I am an IT Support professional transitioning into System Administration and Infrastructure Engineering.

This repository documents hands-on projects completed using Microsoft Azure, Microsoft 365, Entra ID, Intune, Exchange Online, Active Directory, PowerShell, and Security best practices.

Goals:

* Build real-world infrastructure skills
* Develop enterprise administration experience
* Document learning through practical projects
* Create a portfolio demonstrating readiness for System Administrator and Infrastructure Engineer roles

Technologies:

* Microsoft Azure
* Microsoft Entra ID
* Microsoft Intune
* Exchange Online
* SharePoint Online
* Microsoft Teams
* Windows Server
* Active Directory
* PowerShell
* Microsoft Defender

Current Learning Path:
IT Support → System Administrator → Infrastructure Engineer
